<title>CHILE: RESEARCH ALERT-Chile's Polar started buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-Chile's Polar started buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Santander Investment said it started Chilean Coca-Cola bottler Embotelladoras Polar SA with a buy recommendation.</p>
<p>In a report by analysts alexander robarts and heinrich Lessau, Santander said the company had a proven track record in Chile and a well-timed entry into Argentina with the purchase of five franchises.</p>
<p>It estimated earnings per share of 11 Chilean pesos in 1996, 18.4 pesos this year and 24.7 pesos in 1998.</p>
<p>--Santiago newsroom +56-2-6995595 x211</p>
